Code Book for accelerometer and gyroscope 3-axial raw signals
Below is the list of variables included in the tidy data file. In practice I would give a brief description of all of the variables along with their units of measurement.

subject 

activity
  1 WALKING
  2 WALKING_UPSTAIRS
  3 WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS
  4 SITTING
  5 STANDING
  6 LAYING

mean(): Mean value
std(): Standard deviation

